 本帖最后由 lichi2050 于 2016-6-9 11:54 编辑 

用法：用/scoreboard players set @e[type=ArmorStand,c=1] (计分板名称，比如LegMovement) （你要的数值）
 以令装备架作出动作
 由于是高频，所以可能有点卡
 下载连接：百度云
 下一页是这个地图的命令
 ————————————————————————————————
计分板名称/作用（用处：把装备架的这个分数调为你想要的数值和“Timer"分数调为1，便可做出你想要的动作）
 LegMovement 
    1:跑步(会控制左手)
    2 : 走路
    3 : 闪避(向左,装备架的)
    4 : 闪避(向右,装备架的)
 HandMovement:
    1 : 水平斩
    2 : 拔剑术
    3 : 打斜砍
    4 : 垂直砍
    5 : 挥手
    6 : 跑步
 Special
    1 : 射箭（只对"PotatoGuardian”有效）
    2 : 抛出剑
    4 : PM出场（只对PM有效）





生成PotatoGuardian的命令： summon ArmorStand ~ ~1 ~ {NoGravity:0b,Invulnerable:1b,ShowArms:1b,DisabledSlots:0,Pose:{RightArm:[0:2.0f,1:-12.0f,2:0.0f],LeftLeg:[0:0.0f,1:0.0f,2:0.0f],Head:[0:0.0f,1:30.0f,2:0.0f],LeftArm:[0:0.0f,1:-12.0f,2:0.0f],RightLeg:[0:0.0f,1:0.0f,2:0.0f]},Invisible:0b,Rotation:[0:300.0f,1:0.0f],UUIDMost:7290639968733119821L,CustomName:"PotatoGuardian",Equipment:[0:{id:"minecraft:bow",Count:1b,Damage:0s},1:{id:"minecraft:iron_boots",Count:1b,Damage:0s},2:{id:"minecraft:iron_leggings",Count:1b,Damage:0s},3:{id:"minecraft:iron_chestplate",Count:1b,Damage:0s},4:{id:"minecraft:skull",Count:1b,tag:{SkullOwner:{Id:"0DD8BD9D-B65B-C4FF-54D8-25F98344FA68",Properties:{textures:[0:{Value:"e3RleHR1cmVzOntTS0lOOnt1cmw6Imh0dHA6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9xNHNIZzZtLnBuZyJ9fX0=="}]}},display:{Name:"Player Head"}},Damage:3s}],NoBasePlate:1b,CustomNameVisible:0b}

 生成PM的指令： summon ArmorStand ~ ~1 ~ {NoGravity:0b,Invulnerable:0b,ShowArms:1b,DisabledSlots:0,Pose:{RightArm:[0:-100.0f,1:30.0f,2:-180.0f],LeftLeg:[0:0.0f,1:0.0f,2:0.0f],Head:[0:5.0f,1:0.0f,2:0.0f],LeftArm:[0:-80.0f,1:40.0f,2:0.0f],RightLeg:[0:0.0f,1:0.0f,2:0.0f]},Invisible:0b,Small:0b,Equipment:[0:{id:"minecraft:diamond_sword",Count:1b,Damage:0s},1:{id:"minecraft:diamond_boots",Count:1b,Damage:0s},2:{id:"minecraft:diamond_leggings",Count:1b,Damage:0s},3:{id:"minecraft:diamond_chestplate",Count:1b,Damage:0s},4:{id:"minecraft:skull",Count:1b,tag:{SkullOwner:{Id:"cb2671d5-90b8-4dfe-9b1c-73683d451d1a",Properties:{textures:[0:{Signature:"",Value:""}]},Name:"PotatoMaster101"}},Damage:3s}],NoBasePlate:1b} 

计分板设定：
 /scoreboard objectives add TimerLeg dummy
 /scoreboard objectives add LegMovement dummy
 /scoreboard objectives add Timer dummy
 /scoreboard objectives add HandMovement dummy
 /scoreboard objectives add Special dummy

 时间（timer）设定：
 scoreboard players add @e[type=ArmorStand,score_LegMovement_min=1,score_LegMovement=2] TimerLeg 1
 scoreboard players set @e[type=ArmorStand,score_TimerLeg_min=16,score_LegMovement_min=1,score_LegMovement=2] TimerLeg 1
 scoreboard players add @e[type=ArmorStand,score_LegMovement_min=3,score_LegMovement=4] TimerLeg 1
 scoreboard players set @e[type=ArmorStand,score_TimerLeg_min=13,score_LegMovement_min=3,score_LegMovement=4] TimerLeg 1
 scoreboard players add @e[type=ArmorStand,score_HandMovement_min=1,score_HandMovement=5] Timer 1
 scoreboard players set @e[type=ArmorStand,score_Timer_min=7,score_HandMovement_min=1,score_HandMovement=5] Timer 1
 scoreboard players set @e[type=ArmorStand,score_Timer_min=7,score_HandMovement_min=1,score_HandMovement=5] HandMovement 0
 scoreboard players add @e[type=ArmorStand,score_Special_min=1,score_Special=1] Timer 1
 scoreboard players set @e[type=ArmorStand,score_Timer=25,score_Timer_min=25,score_Special_min=1,score_Special=1] Timer 1
 scoreboard players add @e[type=ArmorStand,score_Special_min=2,score_Special=2,score_Timer=7] Timer 1
 scoreboard players add @e[type=ArmorStand,score_Special_min=3,score_Special=3] Timer 1
 scoreboard players add @e[type=ArmorStand,score_Special_min=4,score_Special=4] Timer 1
 scoreboard players set @e[type=ArmorStand,score_Timer_min=6,score_Timer=6,score_Special_min=4,score_Special=4] Special 0


